{"tid":768771,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"減完肥回彈少少係咪正常？","createTime":"2018-08-05T16:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T18:35:35.000Z","uid":159629,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fd2faad768a6245194b453621af96724b88cc7f3","tid":768771,"uid":159629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T16:23:36.000Z","msg":"是咁的，小女子163cm, 原本55kg，<br />\n早半年減肥，個半月減左5公斤，即係50kg。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減肥用5:2輕斷食，非斷食果5日都盡量清淡同1000kcal，<br />\n一星期兩至三次運動，都係跑約30分鐘同負重。<br />\n<br />\n而家體重都Keep住係50-51kg,<br />\n一星期繼續都有2日運動，<br />\n飲食正常，有菜有肉，少食零食/油膩野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但d人話我睇落肥左少少/無之前咁瘦。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n其實減完肥回彈少少正唔正常？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n減完肥要先可以keep到？"},{"pid":"8446f2282b6b50d0327c593e6d305e9a863dd381","tid":768771,"uid":161854,"like":3,"dislike":4,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T16:28:21.000Z","msg":"死肥妹，keep果個半月有Q用 你係要減完起馬要keep到18個月都係差唔多先算穩定 <br />\n <br />\n利申肥仔 230lbs &gt; 165lbs <br />\n一星期游三次水 無戒口任何食物 純計每日卡路里唔過 1800 <br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"f0da74fec070418fde53806cde368f1549a445b7","tid":768771,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T16:29:03.000Z","msg":"死肥妹，keep果個半月有Q用 你係要減完起馬要keep到18個月都係差唔多先算穩定 <br />\n<br />\n利申肥仔 230lbs &gt; 165lbs <br />\n一星期游三次水 無戒口任何食物 純計每日卡路里唔過 1800 <br />\n<br />\n加油"},{"pid":"1ebaff5d9c9ff768ac1246e34dd55d254cea0a27","tid":768771,"uid":18479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T16:36:56.000Z","msg":"水踵？ 我自己會咁 唔知關唔關事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我可以兩日體重相差1kg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a500e8a96e4cd0ddf87c4d24cc7774633b90fd26","tid":768771,"uid":33568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T17:22